com.tomtom.speedtools.mongodb.migratedb

Class MongoDBMigrator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomtom.speedtools.mongodb.migratedb.MongoDBMigrator

  • public abstract class MongoDBMigrator
extends Object
    Class should have an application-specific subclass that registers concrete migrations. Call migrate(MongoDB, boolean) to perform the actual migration.
